Open UBI Platform

	Philosophy

		-
			An open UBI platform, or OUBIP, is an online platform for funding and distributing an
			open UBI.
		-

	Principles

		Open Source

			-
				An OUBIP's source code shall be open source.
			-

		Decentralized OUBIP

			-
				A decentralized OUBIP, or DOUBIP, is an OUBIP that is not managed by any one party
				and is hosted in a decentralized manner.

				Conversely, a centralized OUBIP can be referred to as a COUBIP.
			-